file.name: unique_items.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Sample for uniqueItems
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:3000
paths:
  /unique-items:
    get:
      operationId: unique_items
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Response'
components:
  schemas:
    Response:
      type: object
      properties:
        non-unique-array:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        unique-array:
          type: array
          uniqueItems: true
          items:
            type: string
